
This is a small client to communicate with the https://www.banhosts.com web api which is used to detect and prevent brute force password attacks on services.

* Installing.

	You will need a few extra packages that all major Linux distrubutions already have. This includes the typical auto tool and c++ compilers. You will also need to install libcurl-dev and libjsoncpp-dev in order to compile this from source.

	./autogen.sh && make && sudo make install


	


